reviewText: WE were looking for the history of the rivalry; not just a single game.  is a  history available? PLEASE ADVISE

I was just a little disappointed in ABC's production of Oklahoma vs Texas: College Football's Greatest Rivalries. The actual production itself was adequate, but the host, John Suanders, knew little if anything of the rivalry. Where was Keith Jackson or Brent Musburger? There were a few inaccuracies as well as a few butchered names. ABC gets a "D" on this one.
This DVD is for any college football fan!  Interviews of key players and coaches from both sides of this storied college football rivalry...GREAT!
